Class AbstractEventStorageJdbcImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.AbstractEventStorageJdbcImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AbstractEventStorageJdbc, ApplicationConfiguration, ApplicationModule, EventStorage
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EventStorageJdbcImpl, EventStoragePostgresImpl

    public abstract class AbstractEventStorageJdbcImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements AbstractEventStorageJdbc
    An implementation of the model object 'Abstract Event Storage Jdbc'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Jdbc Properties
    • Schema
    • Instance Name
    • Enable Replication
    • Archive Days
    • Cleanup Period Seconds
